{"4078340": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Happy Hour", "steam_appid": 4078340, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/4719e6ed9f95e55e31c78b4fe2aff7fb.poster.avif?t=1767293949\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/4719e6ed9f95e55e31c78b4fe2aff7fb.webm?t=1767293949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Happy Hour</strong> <br><i>“Step into Chaos”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story-driven adventure where every conversation can turn into chaos, laughter, or desire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/c9abba1b5a7b991bdb4b1811023e5ae2.poster.avif?t=1767293949\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/c9abba1b5a7b991bdb4b1811023e5ae2.webm?t=1767293949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/c9abba1b5a7b991bdb4b1811023e5ae2.mp4?t=1767293949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Characters and Interactions</strong><br><i>“Meet, Talk, and Stir Things Up”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’re surrounded by colorful personalities full of secrets, pasts, and unique traits. Chat, gossip, flirt, or lend a hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/60b42fd719f7b837bc25bf87ff2b6037.poster.avif?t=1767293949\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/60b42fd719f7b837bc25bf87ff2b6037.webm?t=1767293949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/60b42fd719f7b837bc25bf87ff2b6037.mp4?t=1767293949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quests and Charm</strong> <br><i>“Dive into Drama”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on tasks, unravel the tangled web of relationships. Explore jealousy, gossip, and attraction. Forge intimate and fiery connections, and catch the night’s hottest opportunities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/e5b06da9806bd90eb33c2948b8870a54.poster.avif?t=1767293949\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/e5b06da9806bd90eb33c2948b8870a54.webm?t=1767293949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/extras/e5b06da9806bd90eb33c2948b8870a54.mp4?t=1767293949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Control the Night</strong> <br><i>“Your Choices Shape the Night”</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover different paths, complete tasks, and manage your interactions. Your decisions directly affect how the night unfolds and the surprises that appear.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph