. Your decisions directly affect how the night unfolds and the surprises that appear.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ NPC characters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Around 10 quests per character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thousands of dialogue options</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quests and interactive items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non-linear gameplay</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>", "short_description": "A first-person adventure game focused on relationships. Explore the office, meet characters, build and manage connections, and guide the story through your choices.", "supported_languages": "英文<strong>*</strong>, 法文, 義大利文, 德文, 西班牙文 - 西班牙, 簡體中文, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 日文, 韓文, 西班牙文 - 拉丁美洲, 波蘭文, 葡萄牙文 - 葡萄牙, 俄文, 土耳其文, 捷克文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/4c0f9353f032134ab339984dbb5dba589459a4dc/header.jpg?t=1767293949", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/0806a2485a66deae422da652f24931033faa79fc/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1767293949", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4078340/0806a2485a66deae422da652f24931033faa79fc/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1767293949", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows 7+<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Pentium G4500, AMD FX8350 or equivalent<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> Direct X 11 GPU w/ 2GB Available Video Memory<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 8 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "2026"}}}}